---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../../components/Hero.astro';
import FooterCta from '../../components/FooterCta.astro';
export const prerender = true;
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Individual Therapy — Arianna Buratti, Psychologist"
  description="Individual therapy with Arianna Buratti in Carlton, Melbourne. One-on-one support for anxiety, depression, stress, self-esteem, and life transitions."
  activeNav="services"
>

  <Hero
    title="Individual Therapy"
    subtitle="One-on-one psychological support tailored to your needs."
    image="/images/service-individual.jpg"
  />

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container content-section" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <h2>A Safe Space to Talk</h2>
      <hr class="divider" />
      <p>Individual therapy provides a confidential, supportive environment where you can explore your thoughts, feelings, and behaviours with a trained professional. Whether you're dealing with a specific issue or seeking personal growth, therapy offers the tools and space to make meaningful changes.</p>
      <p>I work with adults and young adults on a wide range of concerns, including:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Anxiety and worry</li>
        <li>Depression and low mood</li>
        <li>Stress and burnout</li>
        <li>Self-esteem and confidence</li>
        <li>Life transitions and adjustment</li>
        <li>Grief and loss</li>
        <li>Anger management</li>
        <li>Sleep difficulties</li>
        <li>Health anxiety</li>
        <li>Work-life balance</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--warm">
    <div class="container content-section" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <h2>What to Expect</h2>
      <hr class="divider" />
      <p>In our first session, we'll discuss what brings you in, your goals, and your history. Together, we'll develop a tailored treatment plan using evidence-based approaches such as CBT, ACT, DBT, and Schema Therapy.</p>
      <p>Sessions are typically 50 minutes and can be held weekly or fortnightly depending on your needs. I aim to create a warm, non-judgmental space where you feel comfortable exploring difficult topics at your own pace.</p>
      <p>I also offer <a href="/telehealth/">telehealth sessions</a> for clients who prefer to meet online.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <FooterCta title="Ready to Start?" body="Reach out to book your first session or ask any questions." />

</BaseLayout>
